tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE surveys (
    survey_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    survey_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    question_1 VARCHAR(255),
    question_2 VARCHAR(255),
    question_3 VARCHAR(255),
    question_4 VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE survey_responses (
  response_id INT,
  survey_id INT,
  respondent_id INT,
  question_id INT,
  response_value TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE SurveyData (
    survey_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    survey_name VARCHAR(255),
    survey_date DATE,
    completed BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE QuestionData (
    question_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    survey_id INT,
    question_text TEXT,
    question_type VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE ResponseData (
    response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    survey_id INT,
    question_id INT,
    response_value TEXT,
    response_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE DashboardData (
    dashboard_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dashboard_name VARCHAR(255),
    dashboard_description TEXT,
    created_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE SurveyData (
    survey_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    survey_name VARCHAR(255),
    survey_description TEXT,
    respondent_id INT,
    response_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE Respondents (
    respondent_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    respondent_name VARCHAR(255),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    location VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE SurveyQuestions (
    question_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    survey_id INT,
    question_text TEXT,
    question_type VARCHAR(50),
    options JSON
);

CREATE TABLE Responses (
    response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    survey_id INT,
    respondent_id INT,
    question_id INT,
    response_value TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE DashboardData (
    dashboard_id INT PRIMARY KEY,

    dashboard_description TEXT,
    created_by VARCHAR(100),
    creation_date DATE
);
